  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Main] You may play 1 [ExVeemon] or [Stingmon] from your
    hand without paying the cost. Then, 2 of your Digimon may DNA digivolve into
    a Digimon card in your hand. Until the end of your opponent''s turn, the Digimon
    this effect DNA digivolved can''t be deleted in battle and gains <Blocker>.'
